msgctxt "QL_SearchStone_Desc"
msgid ""
"Garini wants to know what the fragmented\n"
"stone monument said when it was whole.\n"
"\n"
"He's asked you to note down with whatever\n"
"tools you have what each scattered fragment\n"
"of the monument looks like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_SearchStone_Finish"
msgid ""
"You knelt on one platform as Garini took his\n"
"place on the other, causing an ancient shrine\n"
"to appear!\n"
"\n"
"Garini seemed satisfied as he gazed upon the\n"
"new discovery."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_SearchStone_Name"
msgid "A Fragmented Monument"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_SearchStone_Step1"
msgid ""
"You took <1.se_co>pictures <2.re_co>of the scattered fragments\n"
"of the stone monument and showed them\n"
"to Garini.\n"
"\n"
"Once assembled, you discovered that the\n"
"writing on the monument read as follows:\n"
"\n"
"\"When the two find their place and kneel\n"
"in reverence, the shrine will reveal itself.\"\n"
msgstr ""

